OL,3,C'Gentle and kind' father-to-be dies in
OL,4,Ccrash days before Christmas
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a "gentle
OL,7,Fand kind" father-to-be who died in a
OL,8,Fcrash just days before Christmas.
OL,10,FMathew Hardy, 34, was involved in a
OL,11,Fcollision between a car and a truck
OL,12,Fnear Porthmadog in Gwynedd on Saturday
OL,13,Fnight (20 December).
OL,15,FNorth Wales Police said Mr Hardy, from
OL,16,FPwllheli, was pronounced dead at the
OL,17,Fscene.
OL,19,FHis heartbroken family has paid
OL,20,Ftribute to him and revealed that he
OL,21,Fwas soon to be a father to a baby girl.
