OL,3,C'Gentle and kind' father-to-be dies in
OL,4,Ccrash days before Christmas
OL,6,FThe family said: "As a family, our
OL,7,Flives have changed forever, following
OL,8,Fthe incomprehensible loss of Mathew in
OL,9,Fthis horrific tragedy.
OL,11,F"There are no words to describe the
OL,12,Fpain and grief we are feeling. He was
OL,13,Fan incredible son, partner, brother
OL,14,Fand friend, and his absence will leave
OL,15,Fus feeling an emptiness forever.
