OL,3,C'Gentle and kind' father-to-be dies in
OL,4,Ccrash days before Christmas
OL,6,F"Mathew was a gentle, calm and kind
OL,7,Fcharacter who was so deeply loved. He
OL,8,Fwas thrilled to have recently moved
OL,9,Finto a new home, with a baby girl on
OL,10,Fthe way. We truly appreciate
OL,11,Feveryone's kindness and support and
OL,12,Fpolitely ask for privacy during this
OL,13,Fdifficult time."
OL,15,FNorth Wales Police is continuing to
OL,16,Finvestigate the fatal crash and is
OL,17,Fappealing for witnesses to come
OL,18,Fforward.
