OL,3,C'Gentle and kind' father-to-be dies in
OL,4,Ccrash days before Christmas
OL,6,FOfficers are particularly keen to hear
OL,7,Ffrom anyone who may have witnessed or
OL,8,Fhas dashcam footage of events leading
OL,9,Fup to the collision, which involved a
OL,10,FVW Golf and an Isuzu recovery truck.
OL,12,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,13,Fcontact North Wales Police either
OL,14,Fonline or by calling 101, quoting
OL,15,Freference number 25001038987.
